# inside legacy/ submission bundles should still be tracked.
/region.sty
/region.bst
/ERSA_logo.png
/CC-BY-88x31.png

# Stata notebook build artifacts
notebooks/c04_spillover_modeling.log
notebooks/c04_spillover_modeling_table.md

